<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>BadRapApi | Collection of the Worst Rap Lyrics</title>
  <meta name="description"
    content="API for bad rap lyrics. Free to use with unlimited requests. Featuring lyrics from all of your favorite rappers." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Bad Rap Lyrics API" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Send GET requests and get back JSON data. Simple and free to use." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://badrapapi.com" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://badrapapi.com" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="76x76" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png" />
  <link rel="mask-icon" href="/safari-pinned-tab.svg" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark bg-primary p-4">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/" title="Home">
      <img src="/logo.png" alt="logo" width="150" height="50" />
    </a>
  </nav>

  <div class="container-fluid p-0" style="background-color: rgb(13, 110, 253)">
    <h1 class="text-center" style="
          font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
          font-weight: bold;
          color: white;
          padding-top: 50px;
        ">
      API for the Worst Song Lyrics of All Time
    </h1>
    <div class="container" style="
          background-color: rgb(13, 110, 253);
          padding: 75px;
          padding-top: 50px;
        ">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-5 mb-5">
          <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 20px; color: white; padding-right: 10px;">
            A Simple REST API to get some of the funniest song lyrics from all
            your favorite artists. This site only features lyrics so bad they hurt to read. Send a GET request and get
            back a random
            lyric from database, or just browse through all the lyrics stored. Free and easy to use, unlimited requests.
            Some songs may contain
            explicit lyrics.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 text-center mb-5" style="
              margin-bottom: 50px;
              cursor: pointer;
              background-color: rgb(13, 69, 253);
              padding: 25px;
             border-radius: 10px;
            ">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" fill="white" class="bi bi-person"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              d="M8 8a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6zm2-3a2 2 0 1 1-4 0 2 2 0 0 1 4 0zm4 8c0 1-1 1-1 1H3s-1 0-1-1 1-4 6-4 6 3 6 4zm-1-.004c-.001-.246-.154-.986-.832-1.664C11.516 10.68 10.289 10 8 10c-2.29 0-3.516.68-4.168 1.332-.678.678-.83 1.418-.832 1.664h10z" />
          </svg>
          <span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px; color: white; display: block;">Artists</span>
          <p style="color: white">
            Browse all artists featured
          </p>

          <a href="/artists" style="text-decoration: none">
            <div class="btn btn-warning" role="button">
              <span>Browse Artists</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>



    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid" style="background-color: white">
      <div class="container" style="padding-top: 50px">
        <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 35px">Over <code><b><%= homepage_stats.numberOfLyrics %></b></code>
          lyrics across
          <code><b><%= homepage_stats.numberOfArtists %></b></code> artists ranging from
          <code><b><%= homepage_stats.years[0] %>-<%= homepage_stats.years[1] %></b></code>
        </p>

        <%- include('./components/featuredLyrics', { featured_lyrics: featured_lyrics }) %>

          <hr />

          <div >
            <p style="max-width: 850px">
              Our API is incredibly simple to use. It returns JSON data, meaning that it can easily be
              integrated with other applications and websites. It was designed with beginner developers in mind,
              no complicated documentation pages. This API features one
              single endpoint, no need to remember many different routes all returning complicated
              data. All lyrics can be fetched from <code>/api</code>.
            </p>



            <%- include("./components/apiRouteBlock") %>

              <p>You can utilize url query paramters to filter out your search for the perfect lyric. The
                supported filters are:</p>
              <ul>
                <li><code>?artist_query</code></li>
                <li><code>?explicit</code></li>
                <li><code>?year</code></li>

              </ul>
              <p>For example, a random Jay-Z lyric from the year 2003 that does <u>not</u> feature
                explicit language would be <code>/api?artist_query=jayz&explicit=false&year=2003</code>.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-brush"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              d="M15.825.12a.5.5 0 0 1 .132.584c-1.53 3.43-4.743 8.17-7.095 10.64a6.067 6.067 0 0 1-2.373 1.534c-.018.227-.06.538-.16.868-.201.659-.667 1.479-1.708 1.74a8.118 8.118 0 0 1-3.078.132 3.659 3.659 0 0 1-.562-.135 1.382 1.382 0 0 1-.466-.247.714.714 0 0 1-.204-.288.622.622 0 0 1 .004-.443c.095-.245.316-.38.461-.452.394-.197.625-.453.867-.826.095-.144.184-.297.287-.472l.117-.198c.151-.255.326-.54.546-.848.528-.739 1.201-.925 1.746-.896.126.007.243.025.348.048.062-.172.142-.38.238-.608.261-.619.658-1.419 1.187-2.069 2.176-2.67 6.18-6.206 9.117-8.104a.5.5 0 0 1 .596.04zM4.705 11.912a1.23 1.23 0 0 0-.419-.1c-.246-.013-.573.05-.879.479-.197.275-.355.532-.5.777l-.105.177c-.106.181-.213.362-.32.528a3.39 3.39 0 0 1-.76.861c.69.112 1.736.111 2.657-.12.559-.139.843-.569.993-1.06a3.122 3.122 0 0 0 .126-.75l-.793-.792zm1.44.026c.12-.04.277-.1.458-.183a5.068 5.068 0 0 0 1.535-1.1c1.9-1.996 4.412-5.57 6.052-8.631-2.59 1.927-5.566 4.66-7.302 6.792-.442.543-.795 1.243-1.042 1.826-.121.288-.214.54-.275.72v.001l.575.575zm-4.973 3.04.007-.005a.031.031 0 0 1-.007.004zm3.582-3.043.002.001h-.002z" />
          </svg>
          Made by
          <a href="https://awoldt.com/" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none">Awoldt</a></span>
        <a href="/privacy" style="
              display: block;
              text-decoration: none;
              margin-top: 10px;
              margin-bottom: 25px;
            " class="text-secondary">Privacy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>